            <title>[SOLR-3116] new Admin UI does not allow drill-down into ZooKeeper</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3116</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;One thing missing from the old UI for the ZooKeeper view - you can no longer see the data at each node (or at least I have not figured out how) - just the node listing. (Mark Miller, broken out from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2667&quot; title=&quot;Finish Solr Admin UI&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-2667&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-2667&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
